    "en": {
      "title": "Increases the risk of dengue",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The National Dengue Control Unit of the Ministry of Health said that there is a risk of further spread of dengue due to rainy weather.",
        "The Dengue Control Unit has mentioned that 1304 people have been infected with dengue fever in 23 districts across the country in the last week.",
        "The department has also identified Dehiwala, Homagama, Kadualai, Maharagama, Colombo City, Bhattaramulla, EkodaUyana and Kothatuwa as high risk areas where dengue is spreading rapidly."
      ],
